Nolan DEEDS, Appellant,
v.
CITY OF CEDAR RAPIDS; St. Luke's Work Well Solutions ; St. Luke's Healthcare; and Iowa Health System d/b/a Unitypoint Health, Appellees. No. 16-1779 Supreme Court of Iowa. Filed June 22, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

Plaintiff seeks further review of court of appeals decision that affirmed summary judgment dismissing his disability discrimination claims. DECISION OF COURT OF APPEALS AND DISTRICT COURT SUMMARY JUDGMENT AFFIRMED.

DECISION OF COURT OF APPEALS. DISTRICT COURT SUMMARY JUDGMENT AFFIRMED.
